This paper deals with off-policy learning methods for interactive systems, specifically in the context of display advertising. This suggests that the paper is likely to fall under the categories of machine learning (cs.LG), information retrieval (cs.IR), artificial intelligence (cs.AI), data structures and algorithms (cs.DS), and computational engineering, finance, and science (cs.CE).
